      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;public-papers-publications-and-talks&#34;&gt;Public Papers, Publications and Talks&lt;a href=&#34;#public-papers-publications-and-talks&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;kobalos--a-complex-linux-threat-to-high-performance-computing-infrastructure---2021-02&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.welivesecurity.com/2021/02/02/kobalos-complex-linux-threat-high-performance-computing-infrastructure/&#34;&gt;Kobalos – A complex Linux threat to high performance computing infrastructure - (2021-02)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#kobalos--a-complex-linux-threat-to-high-performance-computing-infrastructure---2021-02&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A white paper about an unique multiplatform malware&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;operation-nightscout-supplychain-attack-targets-online-gaming-in-asia---2021-02&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.welivesecurity.com/2021/02/01/operation-nightscout-supply-chain-attack-online-gaming-asia/&#34;&gt;Operation NightScout: Supply‑chain attack targets online gaming in Asia - (2021-02)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#operation-nightscout-supplychain-attack-targets-online-gaming-in-asia---2021-02&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A supply-chain attack used in a cyberespionage operation targeting online‑gaming communities in Asia&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;operation-signsight-supplychain-attack-against-a-certification-authority-in-southeast-asia&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.welivesecurity.com/2020/12/17/operation-signsight-supply-chain-attack-southeast-asia/&#34;&gt;Operation SignSight: Supply‑chain attack against a certification authority in Southeast Asia &amp;rsquo; (2020-12)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#operation-signsight-supplychain-attack-against-a-certification-authority-in-southeast-asia&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A supply-chain attack on the website of a government in Southeast Asia.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;ramsay-a-cyberespionage-toolkit-tailored-for-airgapped-networks---2020-05&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.welivesecurity.com/2020/05/13/ramsay-cyberespionage-toolkit-airgapped-networks/&#34;&gt;Ramsay: A cyber‑espionage toolkit tailored for air‑gapped networks - (2020-05)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#ramsay-a-cyberespionage-toolkit-tailored-for-airgapped-networks---2020-05&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;An implant designed to operate and spread through air-gapped networks&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SKIu4LqMrns&#34;&gt;Presentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.virusbulletin.com/blog/2020/11/vb2020-presentation-ramsay-cyber-espionage-toolkit-tailored-air-gapped-networks/&#34;&gt;WhitePaper&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;linuxrekoobe-operating-undetected---01-2020&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://intezer.com/blog/research/linux-rekoobe-operating-with-new-undetected-malware-samples/&#34;&gt;Linux.Rekoobe Operating Undetected - (01-2020)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#linuxrekoobe-operating-undetected---01-2020&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Rekoobe is a minimalistic trojan with a complex CNC authentication protocol originally targeting SPARC and Intel x86, x86-64 systems back in 2015, reemerging in early 2020.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;elf-crafting-uncovering-advance-anti-analysis-techniques-for-the-linux-platform-r2con2019&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=adYOSO0tn9M&#34;&gt;ELF Crafting. Uncovering Advance Anti-analysis techniques for the Linux Platform (r2con2019)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#elf-crafting-uncovering-advance-anti-analysis-techniques-for-the-linux-platform-r2con2019&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&#xA;      stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;path d=&#34;M15 7h3a5 5 0 0 1 5 5 5 5 0 0 1-5 5h-3m-6 0H6a5 5 0 0 1-5-5 5 5 0 0 1 5-5h3&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;      &lt;line x1=&#34;8&#34; y1=&#34;12&#34; x2=&#34;16&#34; y2=&#34;12&#34;&gt;&lt;/line&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A presentation covering the intricacies of the ELF file format, and how could it be abused by threat-actors to make their malware more challenging to analyze for malware researchers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
